Step 1: Update Template Property in Experience Fragment

To update the cq:template property in the master variation page content node of an Experience Fragment:

Run the below query specifying:

Path to the page content node

Property name: cq:template

New property value

In Action, select:

dryrun to preview affected nodes and current values

node update to apply the change


